posting_body: ['1611', 'On Lake Union', '1611 8th Ave N, Seattle, WA, 98109', 'Need more information?', 'Copy this link:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Live Life On The Lake', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 403 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Conveniently located in South Lake Union, 1611 on Lake Union presents downtown living in an energetic and luxurious setting that is close to everything South Lake Union and Seattle has to offer.', "Don't forget to mention breathtaking views of the lake and a roof top deck for your enjoyment!", "Don't miss out on calling 1611 your home!", 'Call us today!', 'Community Amenities', '- Year-Round Roof Top Deck', '- Gas range Stove*', '- Convenient South Lake Union Location', '- White Quartz Counter Tops', '- All Stainless Steel Appliances', '- Roof Top Fire Pit and BBQ Stations', '- Free Bike Storage', '- New Plank Flooring', '- On-Site Storage Units', '- Controlled Access Building and Parking', '*in select homes', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Saturday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Pet Policy', 'We are pet friendly!', 'Some breed restrictions apply, inquire for more details.', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'apartments Seattle 1611 On Lake Union', 'OIjTTr2i']
